metadata.name: H3VRT
metadata.description:
The artificial Moon creates
a synthetic heart,
recursive jots,
mirror Art.

Light awaits,
where time fails,
a dimension split
from the Tower’s rail.

Keys, codes,
ballads and odes

circulate remote
airy notes
on bloody strings,
moving gypsy rings

for a colossal King,
an evil mobster, who curses
elves, machines and
færie monsters.
